            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"德國稱特朗普已觸及歐洲紅線 必須做好行動準備\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/08MB_RnBYUmtLhFkpQxi1Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/2cb20e60-f52f-11f0-82cb-5e8ac9c1b7a0\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">德國稱特朗普已觸及歐洲紅線 必須做好行動準備</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
