        {
            "title": "日本首相高市早苗確認將於2月8日舉行提前選舉",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"高市早苗攝影師：Kiyoshi Ota/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KlOrf5PGM6ByK9nC53My5A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0df2a02e6aeda7ecdc4856f394f8d384\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">高市早苗攝影師：Kiyoshi Ota/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 日本首相高市早苗計畫在下月的提前選舉中，以臨時下調食品消費稅作為競選主張。該政策在最近兩次全國性選舉中都引起了公眾的共鳴。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高市早苗周一在記者會上確認，將於2月8日舉行提前選舉。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">把食品消費稅降至零並實施兩年的承諾，基本上會剝奪反對黨在選戰中的一張王牌。該承諾此前已被寫入執政陣營協議：高市領導的自由民主黨與執政聯盟的較小夥伴日本維新會簽署了該約定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著提前選舉的啟動，高市似乎押注其較高的個人支持率能夠鞏固她對權力更大的眾議院的掌控。目前執政陣營在眾議院僅享有微弱的過半優勢。若贏得選舉，將使高市獲得公眾授權，以推進更具擴張性的財政政策。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8285d9fa-8982-350a-869e-fd3a04a526c1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Dai-Ichi Life Research Institute經濟學家Hideo Kumano表示：「高市政府在財政紀律方面正在冒險。儘管他們聲稱食品消費稅降為0%僅實施兩年，但我認為一旦實施，幾乎不可能再回到原來的稅率。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《朝日新聞》周末進行的一項民調顯示，高市支持率仍維持在67%的高位；52%的受訪者認為執政陣營料可贏得多數席位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，受訪者中有一半不同意舉行提前選舉，36%支持選舉的時點，50%表示反對。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_hvtlxPCK0xTqzYme8jBmA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/41fdd167d4d5366d5680c47c209a7e97\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan Parties Jostle Over Sales Tax as Takaichi Calls Election</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Momoka Yokoyama、Akemi Terukina.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
